==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trading
<hw>Trad"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Carrying
on trade or commerce; engaged in trade; <as>as, a <ex>trading</ex>
company</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Frequented by traders.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧They on the <xex>trading</xex> flood.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Venal; corrupt; jobbing; <as>as, a <ex>trading</ex>
politician</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tradition</ent>⟦br⟧
